    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-01-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-01-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="72" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d72">
                <head>No. 1.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Stevens</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Foster</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Honolulu, H. I.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-01-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 18, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Via
                                        San Francisco, January 28</hi>. (Received January
                                    28.)</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Events in Hawaii in the past few days have moved rapidly. An entire
                                overthrow of the Hawaiian monarchy and the establishment of a
                                Provisional Government in the interest of the whole people of the
                                islands without the sacrifice of a single life. The new government
                                is in full possession of the islands and was promptly recognized by
                                all the diplomatic representatives. The four men of whom it is
                                composed are of high character, one of whom resigned his position as
                                one of the supreme judges to assume the place. Pull dispatches by
                                the mail leaving Honolulu to-day by special steamer.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stevens</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">United States Minister.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
